  <h2>Important Warnings</h2>
  <div class="warning-box">
    <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Do Not Harass the Defendant</strong>
    You must not harass, threaten, or take the law into your own hands. Always use official court enforcement procedures. Harassment can result in criminal charges and may undermine your legal position.
  </div>

  <div class="warning-box">
